text:
@aleabitoreddit $AXTI just locked in a $22M prepayment from $COHR for 3 years of InP wafers + Beijing capacity ramp through 2028. 

Real money, real commitment in a tight AI photonics supply chain.

Fundamentals look better, but semis are still getting crushed.

